DBI/Simple version 0.01
=======================

DBI::Simple allows easy access to the DBI.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   DBI and any appropriate DBD modules.

